Install Angular
	npm install --save @angular/cli

For version
	ng --version

Create a project
	ng new angular_app_name

Press Y for create routers. Then Choouse your style Type(CSS).

To run angular Server (Before Run this go in to the forlder)
	ng serve

Add components
	ng generate component componant-path-from-app-and-name
OR
	ng g c componant-path-from-app-and-name
